\section{Global Variables}

\begin{itemize}
    \item \texttt{isPasswordVisible}: Boolean flag
    \item \texttt{iconSize = 40}: Consistent icon size
\end{itemize}

\section{Design Philosophy}

\begin{itemize}
    \item Dark theme UI
    \item Orange accents
    \item Times New Roman typography
\end{itemize}

\chapter{Image Handling and Caching}

\section{Overview}

A custom widget \texttt{CachedProfileImage} handles image loading and caching.

\subsection{1. Image Source Detection}
Local assets vs remote images are automatically detected.

\subsection{2. Caching}
Remote images cached via \textbf{CachedNetworkImage}.

\subsection{3. Display Options}
Supports:
\begin{itemize}
    \item Circular avatars
    \item Rectangular images
\end{itemize}

\subsection{4. Loading and Error Handling}
\begin{itemize}
    \item Circular progress indicator during load
    \item Error icon if image fails
\end{itemize}

\chapter{Backend API Service Integration}

\section{Authentication}

The \texttt{ApiService} class handles communication with backend:

\begin{itemize}
    \item \texttt{testConnection()}
    \item \texttt{login(email, password)}
    \item \texttt{register(username, email, password)}
\end{itemize}

\section{User Profile Management}

\begin{itemize}
    \item Update username
    \item Upload profile picture
    \item Retrieve profile picture
\end{itemize}

\section{Recipe Operations}

\begin{itemize}
    \item \texttt{getRecipes()}
    \item \texttt{uploadRecipe()}
\end{itemize}

\chapter{Local Database (SQLite)}

\section{Database Structure}

The app uses \textbf{sqflite} with the following fields:

\begin{itemize}
    \item id, name, category, time, calories
    \item image
    \item ingredients (JSON)
    \item mood (JSON)
    \item difficulty
    \item steps (JSON)
    \item isFavorite
\end{itemize}

\section{Core Operations}

\begin{itemize}
    \item \texttt{getRecipes()}
    \item \texttt{getFilteredRecipes()}
    \item \texttt{toggleFavorite()}
\end{itemize}

\chapter{Data Models}

\section{Recipe Model}

Fields include:
\begin{itemize}
    \item id, name, category, time, calories
    \item imagePath
    \item ingredients, steps, moods
    \item isFavorite
\end{itemize}

\section{User Model}

Fields include:
\begin{itemize}
    \item id
    \item username
    \item email
    \item profileImage
    \item joinedDate
\end{itemize}

\chapter{State Management With Providers}

\section{RecipeProvider}

Manages:
\begin{itemize}
    \item Recipes list
    \item Favorites
    \item Loading and error states
\end{itemize}

\section{UserProvider}

Handles:
\begin{itemize}
    \item Authenticated user
    \item Profile updates
    \item Logout
\end{itemize}

