Images organized under assets folder.

\chapter{Conclusion}

PickMyDish is a feature-rich and user-friendly mobile platform that simplifies food decision-making by combining mood analysis, ingredient filtering, and time-based recommendations. The project uses a clean architecture, robust backend integration, local caching, SQLite storage, and a visually appealing UI built with Flutter.

